headline: Stocks Drop Again. Nasdaq Falls for Fourth Straight Session.
summary: The stock market opened lower again on Friday as the Nasdaq Composite selloff entered its fourth day. The Dow Jones Industrial Average fell 531 points, or 1.1%. The S&P 500 was down 1.3%. The Nasdaq Composite was down 1.
